  "sections": [],
  "kind": "article",
  "abstract": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Adjust your app’s behavior and filter incoming notifications when the"
    },
    {
      "text": " ",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "current Focus changes."
    }
  ],
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "anchor": "Overview"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "image",
              "identifier": "focus-filters-hero"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "People use Focus on macOS, iOS, and iPadOS to minimize distractions. For example,"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "someone might use a Work Focus to hide notifications from personal email"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "or message accounts. When someone engages a Focus, the system executes your"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "app’s custom ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/SetFocusFilterIntent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Define a version of this intent to"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "update your app’s configuration and filter incoming notifications.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Session 10121: "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022/10121",
                  "isActive": true
